snippet: A day after a lead prosecutor was fatally shot in an employee parking lot near his office, the police said they had no motive or suspects.
abstract: Police have no motives nor have identified any suspects in murder of Kaufman, Tex, prosecutor Mark E Hasse, who was shot multiple times in employee parking lot near his office;  officials say they are investigating possible connections to cases victim worked on.

byline.original: By LAUREN D'AVOLIO and MANNY FERNANDEZ

lead_paragraph: A day after a lead prosecutor was fatally shot in an employee parking lot near his office, the police said they had no motive or suspects.

headline.seo: No Suspects Identified in Texas Prosecutor’s Shooting
headline.main: No Suspects Are Identified in Texas Prosecutor’s Death
headline.print_headline: No Suspects Are Identified In Texas Prosecutor’s Death
